content: As an AI, I don't have personal preferences or emotions, so I don't have a favorite Beatles song. However, "Hey Jude," "Let it be," "Yesterday," "All You Need Is Love," "A Hard Day's Night," "Help!," "Come Together," "Twist and Shout," and "Here Comes The Sun" are some of their most popular and timeless songs that are loved by fans all around the world.
